==Hindi==
===Pronunciation===
/ je: /

===Demonstrative pronoun===
'''ये''' (ye)

# [[these]] - direct case only, see below for oblique. (Singular: [[यह]])
#:Example: "ये [[मकान]] बड़े [[हैं]]" - This house is large
# [[he]] - direct case only, honorific. (If no additional [[respect]] is conveyed, यह is used)
#:Example: "ये छोटे हैं" - He is small
# [[she]] - direct case only, honorific. (If no additional [[respect]] is conveyed, यह is used)
#:Example: "ये छोटी हैं" - She is small
# [[they]] near reference and direct case only. [[वे]] is the far reference for someone farther away from the speaker
#:Example: "ये [[कौन]] हैं?" - Who are they?

====Inflection====
[[Oblique]]: [[इन]]

